  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the clinical efficacy and cost-effectiveness of the ACQUIRE-ICD care
      innovation as add-on to usual care as compared to usual care alone in patients with an
      implantable cardioverter defibrillator.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
